Hello Ines

This is not how the builds of accepted packages work. 

The builds run once a day, and depending when the builders pull the contents from git.bioconductor.org (see date and time at the top of https://master.bioconductor.org/checkResults/3.13/bioc-LATEST/index.html), your changes may not be reflected in that build yet.

Regards,
Michael

